To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private IdenticalThreeCrows _identicalthreecrows;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_identicalthreecrows = IdenticalThreeCrows(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_identicalthreecrows.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "IdenticalThreeCrows Period", _identicalthreecrows.Period);
    Plot("My Indicators", "IdenticalThreeCrows Current", _identicalthreecrows.Current);
